## Identidad del team

- **Workshop:** {{WORKSHOP_NAME}}
- **Team ID:** {{TEAM_ID}}
- **Dominio:** {{TEAM_DOMAIN}}
- **Members:** {{TEAM_MEMBERS}}
- **App path:** `apps/{{TEAM_ID}}/`
- **API prefix:** `/api/{{TEAM_ID}}`
